{"tid":685551,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［機會難得］德軍軍糧3號餐單開箱試食！","createTime":"2018-05-31T13:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T09:38:19.000Z","uid":10717,"like":149,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"ad705a20e4fc59f828fe40c226410e1ff828b342","tid":685551,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"之前已經食過俄佬，英國軍糧，今次香港某鋪頭入左少量德國軍糧，拿拿聲放工之後仆去買黎試食！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/203407_fceec945dcf25b50f7fde8ef046384eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F203407_fceec945dcf25b50f7fde8ef046384eb.png&h=50346d91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次買左2盒，1盒自己食1盒幫人買<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/203536_427a11829c78abacb91a19e42c87716b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F203536_427a11829c78abacb91a19e42c87716b.png&h=5e1eb145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國野真係德國野，連野食都分得咁整齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/203647_54067e5af1ec2f757c24e7e9b800ec32.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F203647_54067e5af1ec2f757c24e7e9b800ec32.png&h=eab84a12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/203652_f57aefcef72b3f86150494db598dc523.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F203652_f57aefcef72b3f86150494db598dc523.png&h=8cb98d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主餐<br />\nready to eat turkey medallions<br />\n主要有火雞薯仔蘿蔔青豆<br />\n一開已經有好香既洋蔥同牛油味<br />\n鹹淡啱啱好，薯仔有咬口<br />\n唯一敗筆火雞比較鞋身<br />\n如果有碗飯喺度幾好呢<br />\n9.5/10<br />\n但我覺得呢個主食已經正過英軍同俄佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/205306_8e4b4a96b61ca0d6a3db69ca69ce3247.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F205306_8e4b4a96b61ca0d6a3db69ca69ce3247.png&h=e8628239&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/205314_efd4f92a51608557279f09c6037dd7ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F205314_efd4f92a51608557279f09c6037dd7ff.png&h=85ec1b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210229_92ddf177cbd2ff87325a343711b7467a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210229_92ddf177cbd2ff87325a343711b7467a.png&h=4604a238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n臭名昭著的黑麥麵包<br />\n一如網上軟的同松而且有浸霉味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就咁食咗一啖好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n0.1/10<br />\n惟一開左的牛肉香腸去搽黎食<br />\n終於叫正常<br />\n<br />\n牛肉香腸同平時食既五餐肉差唔多<br />\n6/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210254_039b3a58af1f54abc0ca2c606638c638.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210254_039b3a58af1f54abc0ca2c606638c638.png&h=5c73389e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210326_81c894c0af2ce1e0ee6324e8e6264e7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210326_81c894c0af2ce1e0ee6324e8e6264e7a.png&h=0ad2fe59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210332_5e8af5ab9b7101cc663fc926331c6fbb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210332_5e8af5ab9b7101cc663fc926331c6fbb.png&h=45abd042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比較硬既克力架，但是嚼起來有少少甜味，而且聞起來亦香<br />\n桃同士多啤梨醬食落去還可以<br />\n6/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210649_7b8c6103494d85a4f96fa5f0d71897f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210649_7b8c6103494d85a4f96fa5f0d71897f0.png&h=35af66ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開左2包德國水黎飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210835_900493bcaa83bf1eef4bc579a2a81f3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210835_900493bcaa83bf1eef4bc579a2a81f3a.png&h=08c5fca7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/210846_1410f49d4c0e9ca6c4b89923dc50f979.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F210846_1410f49d4c0e9ca6c4b89923dc50f979.png&h=d94cda90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱古力<br />\n好香嘅可可味<br />\n食落去比較甜同濃味<br />\n6/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/211707_0b21c2217b2cddd07e45e9ca02683f2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F211707_0b21c2217b2cddd07e45e9ca02683f2d.png&h=662c63d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好難頂嘅能量飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聞落藥水味<br />\n咁落好甜同有少少酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1/10<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/211519_b9f01be7061df41be06416bb46fcc5a9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F211519_b9f01be7061df41be06416bb46fcc5a9.png&h=f3a8aebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茶同咖啡聽日再試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48919588d07c73f2a5cb737c4f6753eed84738e","tid":685551,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"Ching, 軍迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4080d997e7281ab0ab385d2cffea70a4e987dd34","tid":685551,"uid":182397,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0216a42ac3b7b2404b5d57be56519a4208c99918","tid":685551,"uid":58321,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"kfc雞皇飯白汁加強版？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4996ef4ff8026e8808f23cd7d198cacdacc8110","tid":685551,"uid":27568,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"一如網上軟的同松而且有浸霉味<br />\n<br />\n同松即係點<br />\n<br />\n一盒係全日糧食?"},{"pid":"8e1d038920e6931dae30db58d83c3e45a1c31d88","tid":685551,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4080d997e7281ab0ab385d2cffea70a4e987dd34","tid":685551,"uid":182397,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0e442d36c289564a779aea0e0864feec74eac5","tid":685551,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T13:51:24.000Z","msg":"啲朱古力唔苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953fdc3667c50764943071fcc2ec139fa5898d13","tid":685551,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4996ef4ff8026e8808f23cd7d198cacdacc8110","tid":685551,"uid":27568,"like":1,"disl